AddressInfo.Title: Dicks RV Park
AddressInfo.AccessComments: I-5 exit 278. Open year around 24/7.Stay at the campground if you want, or Best Western Heritage Inn hotel across the street. Hotel van driver will pick you up, if you check into the hotel first. or you can walk across street to hotel.  Staff is EV friendly.

GeneralComments: online reservations are available, but seem to not always work. might want to call ahead of time and have Credit card to reserve.  bring both 110v standard an 220v nema 14-50 adaptor as sometimes (according to comments on other sites), this place is full for RVs and the push EV drivers to slow chargers.
